  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">1380 children research on rurality of Colombia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Schools in Southwestern Antioquia, Colombia, do not have a scientific culture. To solve this 90 researching groups conformed by 1380 poor children have been made up for them to research starting from their own questions in different areas. This will make children understand their relationship with the world with a critical perspective; and teachers in schools be able to impact the content of the classes, curriculum and educational quality thanks to the inlcusion of research in learning dynamics</narrative>
  </description>
